channel.description:

For some reason it's just those swords Im not sure if it's a new update with those swords (I hope not) but if anyone can tell me a solution to this if there is i'd be thankful.
Oh yeah i also need help with the pickup command i tried about three different codes for it none of them worked. I'm using the blank silab source so if there's a second part to the pickup command can you tell me it and where to add it? if any of you have a solution to this THANK YOU
